Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:03.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the powers of the Soul Reaper\Nwere thrust upon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my whole world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:07.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Substitute Soul Reaper,\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:11.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wield this sword\Nwith all of my soul and strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:14.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to protect my precious friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:25.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:31.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one can take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:36.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never fade, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:49.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun never blinds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.72,0:00:55.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a flower that blooms in shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:01:05.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Exhale those feelings you hold inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:15.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only;\Nnow and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:25.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The day may come\Nwhen all will rise against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:30.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:34.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never give up, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:41.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,TIME NOTICE THAT\NYOU SHOULD NOTICE THAT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:45.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,NOTICE THAT THERE’S NO OTHER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:09.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:14.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:31.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, that bastard.\NHe's just acting tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he's not thinking that\Nhe doesn't want to be a burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing away his own friends…\NThat's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:41.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:44.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! It's not even trash day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:47.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're mad? That's unusual…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:52.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I'm going to find him\Nand treat his wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:41.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:46.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I had used the last of\Nmy strength, maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:03:59.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I could have thrown her off my trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:14.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:15.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:19.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you had lonely eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:23.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a good enough answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're being targeted by the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:39.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be putting your friends\Nin danger if you stayed with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:42.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a sad story…\NNo one's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you felt sorry for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:55.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem like the type\Nwho would be sentimental like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:59.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was once like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time when\NI saw sweet sentimental dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those feeling have just become cold…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:10.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,because of the mind-numbing\Npassage of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's some noise…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel it echoing\Nthrough my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:25.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're not used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:30.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to hearing it,\Nso I no longer feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:35.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the bells\Nor the passing of time…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:42.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you've watched\Nthis town all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:46.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uninvolved with anyone and all alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Strangely…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:51.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lack of reality when…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:54.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I watch those people restlessly\Nliving from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:56.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you even live with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time when I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was a long time ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A long time…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:18.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For a time so long that it numbs the mind,\Nwe've lived in the shadow of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:20.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,During that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,countless numbers of us\Nhave endured harsh experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:25.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and borne indescribable treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With that behind us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:31.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the time when we Bounts can\Nbe released from the darkness…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:34.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is finally approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This long time…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:43.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,may be what plants fleeting dreams\Nand foolish ambition in us Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everything…because of time…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:47.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You hate time so much…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you live next to this clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:07:00.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you're still\Nexpecting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:04.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You want to live rather\Nthan observe the passage of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:09.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If it's possible…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I'd like to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Die?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:21.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When you have eternal life,\Nyou feel like you can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:24.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You begin to think that\Nyou've become a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:26.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:32.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then…\NKariya could you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:35.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you gathered us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Quincy has been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:42.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:46.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:52.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We chosen Bounts\Nmust catch this Quincy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:58.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To gain greater absolute power…\Nand for our shining era!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:04.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maki Ichinose's Spiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:08.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It has been undeniably\Nconfirmed to be in the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:09.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Aramaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:15.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've never been able to find him,\Nno matter how hard we looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:18.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We were suddenly able to\Ntrack his Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:23.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard Captain Hitsugaya and\NCaptain Ukitake talking about it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, then, Maki-maki…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is Maki in\Nthe World of the Living right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:32.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so, Maki-maki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maki is alive, Maki-maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:36.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:41.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but that's confusing,\Nso could you not repeat my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:46.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?\NYou're Maki-maki and Maki is Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:47.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're completely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that it's confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:54.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t the nickname Maki-maki…\Nkind of weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… I mean, don't ask me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:59.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:08.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel a bit responsible…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:11.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ken-chan, don't you feel it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:39.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zaraki… You…\NHow dare you do this to the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:41.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, Ichinose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:52.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Under the attendance\Nof 200 squad members,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:53.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the winner of this match and\Nthe new captain of Squad Eleventh is…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenpachi Zaraki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't allowed to draw\Nyour sword here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How boring…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:06.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, all of you!\NI'm going to do things my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:11.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't chase those who leave!\NDo as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.59,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:22.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re still holding\Na grudge against Ken-chan…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:26.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… That was an official\None-on-one match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:29.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Zaraki did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:37.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I really can’t find\Na reason to remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Also…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:47.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My captain will always…\Nbe our former captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:06.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, he looked\Nas if he would just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably being forced to live…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know who’d do that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:26.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ichinose, what do you suppose\NKariya's real objective is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What does he plan to do when\Nhe catches the Quincy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:33.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? I do not question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:36.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I simply obey Master Kariya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's easier that way…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:44.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you always completely\Nagree or disagree…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:46.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there's no reason to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:55.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…\NI'm still thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:11.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:13.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:28.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…\NWhere in the world did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is miserable here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:53.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should put…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:56.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I try not to own things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:58.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:01.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much of a burden\Nto own things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:04.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when the things\Nyou should be thankful for…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:11.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,feel like a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Another day is about to end…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:27.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I look down at humans\Nfrom here, I think…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:31.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we live for hundreds of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:34.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are so short-sighted\Ncompared to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:38.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that short-sightedness…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:42.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's because people only\Nhave a few decades
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in which they can try hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:56.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when I was still a child…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:07.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I came to have this odd feeling that\NI was not like normal people…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:13.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I've kept that fact a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:22.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was desperate to keep that…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:25.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a secret even from\Nmy friends…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:30.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But then I realized…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:33.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that it was impossible for them\Nnot to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:51.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around me\Nwas aging like they should.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:53.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,People…and history…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:57.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like only\NI was left behind…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:15:01.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never changing.\NUnable to change…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:03.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was at such a loss…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:08.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time had passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:11.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was forever left behind\Nby the times…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Find her! Find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:21.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a witch!\NShe's got to be a witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kill her! Kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:27.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I had tired of living…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:32.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Day by day I thought only\Nof ways to die…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:38.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And when I decided to\Nend my own life…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:56.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be afraid…\NI'm like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:15:59.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:03.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to live with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:05.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He said there were reasons\Nfor Bounts like us to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:31.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you my reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:36.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:48.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Bount's love is deep, long…\Nlimitless, and continues eternally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:56.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,God has given Bounts\Nour time of bliss…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:14.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal love…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:18.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time when\NI truly believed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:27.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've realized that\Nthe word “eternal”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:33.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,exists for humans who\Nhave limited life spans…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:37.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that has\Nno meaning to us Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:43.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,does that mean that\Nyour love for him…Kariya…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,came to an end?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:50.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There may not have been\Nany love to begin with…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:56.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The light of hope\NI saw was an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:03.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He tricked my eyes with\Na bright veil of light…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,only to hide his ambition\Nin its shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:08.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ambition?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Power Hold…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:17.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya has gathered\Nthe few Bounts that are left…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and is probably trying\Nto go to Hueco Mundo…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:24.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to gain\Nlimitless power there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:31.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make the Bounts…\Nno, himself an ultimate god!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:34.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If he does that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:38.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he'll deviate from the principal rules\Nwhich we must uphold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:41.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,God has no rules to follow…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:44.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rules are for God to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:45.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even so!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:50.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've brought you here.\NTo keep Kariya from doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:55.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… Do you…\Nstill love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive him…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:05.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order for me to remain human,\Nhowever little that may be…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive him for losing\Nhis human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:11.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He took a living person's soul…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with the same mouth with\Nwhich he told me he loved me…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:36.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive Kariya for that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:41.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't forgive myself even more\Nfor being unable to stop him…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:46.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:50.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me the hope to live,\Nbut by his betrayal, I awakened to…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:55.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the little that remained of my heart\Nas a human which slept within me…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:59.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat Kariya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:04.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:07.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd help you if I could but,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer can…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are kind\Nto want to help me…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:17.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I don’t intend to rely\Non you any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:24.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should just stay in this room\Nuntil your wounds heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any hope of winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:27.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:34.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If it's possible, I'd like to die…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:35.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:45.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:50.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to be captured\Nby Kariya's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:52.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:56.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but you're a key person\Nin Kariya's goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I no longer have any powers…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:02.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:03.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:10.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have the feeling that\Nthe Quincy power still lies within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:16.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:21.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:25.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing\NI realized earlier…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:33.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I could have run away from you\Nif I had wanted to…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:37.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now I finally know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:42.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:44.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:52.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I may have seen a small ray of hope\Nfrom your lonesome eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:56.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't fallen completely\Ninto despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:59.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have a beautiful light\Nthat seeks hope…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:05.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well… If it's possible,\NI'd like to help you…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:08.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I can do\Nin this condition, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:09.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even so…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:13.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:22.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are good-natured\Ndespite your looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.72,0:22:42.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:44.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:47.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:54.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time goes by, and I get left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:57.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say,\N“don’t forget that anxious feeling”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:23:00.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They tell me,\N“A reckless challenge is meaningless”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:02.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say “don’t give up.”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.51,0:23:12.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) At times when\Nthe going gets tough, I raise my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:22.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) And head toward\Nthe direction of my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:32.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be afraid of\Nthat towering wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:42.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never losing sight in this life\Nwithout answers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:45.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep My Pace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:55.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.59,0:23:58.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:24:00.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.80,0:24:05.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.69,0:24:09.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Soul Reaper\Namong the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.62,0:24:11.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably a good-for-nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.35,0:24:13.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Probably a dangerous battle maniac\Nor a crazy-eyed modification maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:15.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Who might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.80,0:24:17.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear more.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:22.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:33.67,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Illustrated Guide\Nto Soul Reapers after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.71,0:24:35.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.13,0:24:36.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.28,0:24:38.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Health Land
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.79,0:24:41.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to go to Health Land\Nto do our remaining business?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.97,0:24:47.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?! Let's meet in the rest space\Nand work after a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.47,0:24:49.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be more productive!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.52,0:24:50.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.53,0:24:55.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry. Children must stay\Nwith their guardians.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.64,0:24:59.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Child… Child…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.03,0:25:01.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Then let's go\Nin the women's bath together!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.40,0:25:03.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.65,0:25:11.65,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tune in again!